  "body": "\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.8.0-unstable`\r\nOS & Version: OSX\r\nCommit hash : 1c2378b926b4ae96ae42a4e802058a2fcd42c87b\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nStart node one using: \r\ngeth --datadir ~/.ethereum/poa init poa.json\r\ngeth --datadir ~/.ethereum/poa --unlock 0xxxx --mine --rpcaddr 127.0.0.1 --rpcapi eth,net,web3,personal  console\r\n\r\nStart node two using: \r\ngeth --datadir ~/.ethereum/poa1 init poa.json\r\ngeth --datadir ~/.ethereum/poa1 --port 30304 console --unlock 0xxxx\r\n\r\nOn node one type:\r\nadmin.addPeer(\"enode://xxx\")\r\nclique.propose(\"0xxxx\", true)\r\n\r\nOn node two start mining:\r\nminer.start()\r\n\r\nExpect node one print out:\r\nINFO [01-05|xx:xx:xx] Signed recently, must wait for others\r\nINFO [01-05|xx:xx:xx] Imported new chain segment               blocks=1  txs=0 mgas=0.000 elapsed=539.557µs mgasps=0.000 number=21 hash=4680a4…ec6a25\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nINFO [01-05|xx:xx:xx] Signed recently, must wait for others\r\nWARN [01-05|xx:xx:xx] Discarded bad propagated block           number=15 hash=b2f244…b5a265\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nInitiate the genesis with only node one's account\r\n\r\n\r\n  ",
